    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, though upon close inspection, you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is clean and free of tears, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. You can expect a solid, dependable ride that looks great from a distance and shows only the expected signs of careful use.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
