      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, sporting a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely zero imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in untouched condition; the premium leather is supple with no wear on the bolsters, and every electronic feature functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive binder of every service interval performed exclusively by certified technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a pristine undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands perfection without compromise. Truly turn-key and ready for its next steward.",
      "price": 48500.0,
